I don’t know what has happened to the outpost, as I have been wandering around for a while. The outpost was destroyed, covered in a green liquid, and was wrecked apart. I hear screams from someone, a fellow comrade of mine, being torn apart in pieces; that's when the slaughter started. I saw many get killed by the wendigo like entity, right in front of my eyes, while other members collapsed from the radioactive smog.

I think..well hopefully think that some fled to other levels. I'd like to think that I wasn't the unlucky one..the one that wouldn't be stranded and knew their way to the exit, where I just hope that's true, cause I think I'm starting to lose it. I keep seeing things, I don't know if they're real but I keep seeing an unknown entity inch closer and closer- Oh wait..I see someo[[File:Scribble.png|frameless]]

